                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-287-off1586 t18180909-287-cd1587"></join>, one sheet, value 7s.; four handkerchiefs, value 2s.; three shirts, value 7s.; three pair of stockings, value 4s., and one apron, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180909-287-victim2017" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
